{
  "stem": "6258.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Alexander Weissberg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he was arrested during the big purges by Stalin, he-- every Nobel Prize winner, Joliot-Curie, the daughter and his wife, and [INAUDIBLE], and including Albert Einstein, they wrote to Stalin about Alexander Weissberg that this must be a mistake, that he absolutely could not be involved in killing Stalin or Molotov or whatever.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, it was no answer whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, he was so every day in this inquiry by-- by the KBG and so forth for two years or more.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- but nothing ever happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they keep him and exchange him with some other German and some other Jews who were there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they give them into the German hands at the beginning of the war, because they were sure that they will kill them, the German will kill them all.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Weissberg run away from the transport in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came into the Jewish-- into the Krakow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, this is how he met me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was in-- in that Polish Underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Being a physicist, he was preparing all kind of, you know, these things to spraying, the bombs and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he wanted badly take me out of the  ghetto and, you know, in order to save me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I would never part with my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I stay in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He just disappear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When he disappear, he went and was-- first he was fighting later on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because this was also '42, in Jewish, well, uprising in Warsaw in the ghetto, and then in Polish uprising in ghetto in-- not in ghetto, but in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And later on, he was saved by a Polish aristocratic woman with whom he later lived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cybulski, Sophia Cybulski, C-Y-B-U-L-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C, like Cecilia.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
